      "text": "Sihne/ ko es eezehts esmu starp\nman/ un starp wiſfas Meefas/ kas\nwiſs Semmes irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Noũs Dehli / kas no\nSchirſta iſgahje / bija / Sems/\nun Kams/ un Jawets/ un Kains\niir Kanãna Tehws.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee trihs irr Noũs\nDehli / un no ſcheem irr wiſfa\nSemme eedſihwota.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Noũs tahze to Semmi\nkohtt/ un Wthna-Dahrsu ſtrah-\ndaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch dſehre no ta\nWihtna/ un apdſehrabs/ un gul-\nleja atſedſees ſawa Dſihwoſta\nWiddũ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Kams/ Kanãana Tehws\nredſeja ſawa Tehwa plikks Mee-\nfas/ un paſazzija to ſaweem di-\nwt Brahteem ahra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehine Sems un Ja-\nwets Drehtes/ un likke tahs us\nſaweem abbejeem Plezzeim / un\natſchagarni etjoht apſedſe tee ſa-\nwa Tehwa plikks Meeſas/ un\ntee bij ſawu Waigu nogreesſchi/\nka tee ſawa Tehwa plikks Mee-\nfas ne redſeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Noũs uſmohdahs no\nſawa Wihtna/ un fajutte/ ko wiꞥ-\nra masajs Dehls winnam bij\ndarrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija : Notahdehts\nlaid irr Kanãans / tam buhs ſa-\nwo Brahtu Kalpo Kalpam buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Sweh-\ntihts irr tas KUNGS/ Sema\nDeews/ un Kanãans lai irr win-\nra Kalps.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai Deewß iſplatta to Ja-\nwetu / un tai tas dſihwo Sema\nDſihwoſtõs/ un Kanians lai irr\nwinna Kalps.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Noĩis dſihwoja pehz\nteem Uhdens-Pluhdeein trihs-\nſiuts un peezdetmits Gaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad bija wiſfas Noũs\nDeenas dewinsints un peezdeſ-\nmits Gaddi/ un wiſch nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta X. Nodalla.\nStahſti no Noĩis Behrno un pehzmahkamo\nDſintas un Wairoſchanas: 1. Jaweta Rad-\ndi : 2. Kama Raddi : 6. Nimrods bija\nwarrer: iſs Waldneefs wiſs Semmes/ un jah-\nze Babelã waldiht : 8. Ajur uſtaifa Mini-\nwu : Sema Raddi : z1.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nfchee irr tee Stahſti\nno Noũs Dehlu Dſim-\ntahm/(arWahrdeem)\nSems/ Kams un Jawets / un\nteem dſimina Dehli pehz teem Uh-\ndens-Pluhdeein.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jaweta Behrni irr : Go-\nmersun Magogs/ un Madajus,\nun Jawans / un Tuhbals / un\nMeseks/ un Tihras.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gomera Behrni (ir-\nfchee :) Askenas/ un Rihwats\nun Togarmas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jawana Behrni (ir-\nfchee :) Elisus / un Tarsis / un\nKihtims un Dodanins.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No ſcheem irr iſplattita\nto Pagaxu Sallas ſawas Sem-\nmes Teefãs/ itweens pehz ſawa\nWalloas / pehz ſawas Zilts\nstarp ſawahin Tautahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kama Behrni irr : Kuṣ\nun Mizrãims/ un Puts/ un Ka-\nnãns.\n"
    }
  ],
